UnicodeDecodeError: 'utf8' codec can't decode byte 0x8b in position 1: invalid start byte

I fixed this error updating youtube-dl file on gem bin directory:

Steps:
1. Download script:
wget https://yt-dl.org/downloads/2014.12.17.2/youtube-dl
2. In my case:
$ cp youtube-dl /home/adrian/.rvm/gems/ruby-2.1.3/gems/youtube_dl-0.0.2/bin
